                            <h3>How it works</h3>
                            <p>WaterCredit is a powerful solution and the first to put microfinance tools to work in the
                                water and sanitation sector. WaterCredit helps bring small loans to those who need
                                access to affordable financing and expert resources to make household water and toilet
                                solutions a reality.</p>
                            <p><b>Here’s how it works:</b></p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>We identify a region where people need access to water and sanitation and that is
                                    ready for a microfinance solution.</li>
                                <li>We partner with carefully selected institutions to provide affordable financing for
                                    water and sanitation to families in need.</li>
                                <li>These microfinance partners establish water and sanitation loans in their portfolio
                                    of offerings. We support them by providing technical assistance, connections and
                                    resources to get them started.</li>
                                <li>People in need use these small, affordable loans to put a tap or toilet in their
                                    homes and access local resources to do the work.</li>
                                <li>Every repaid loan can be lent to another family in need of safe water or sanitation.
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
